WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.712
You won't see him no more.

00:00:01.920 --> 00:00:04.559
- Where are you going?
- To the city.

00:00:04.760 --> 00:00:07.991
- Send bodyguards with him.
- I'm going to the hospital...

00:00:08.200 --> 00:00:11.237
He'll be all right.
Sollozzo knows he's a civilian.

00:00:11.440 --> 00:00:14.034
- Be careful.
- Yes, sir.

00:00:16.280 --> 00:00:18.396
Send somebody with him anyway.

